--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 1.0.5 (2020-12-09)
B: Correct EPEL GPG key file name (RPM-GPG-KEY-EPEL-8)

* Version 1.0.4 (2020-12-08)
E: Adapt configuration to new repository names introduced with CentOS 8.3.2011

* Version 1.0.3 (2020-10-30)
E: Simplify Ansible file header (ansible_managed)

* Version 1.0.2 (2020-06-30)
E: Do not manage directory local_sbin.dir (/usr/local/sbin)

* Version 1.0.1 (2020-06-29)
B: Only remove script file and not directory
E: Rename script directory variable name

* Version 1.0.0 (2020-06-29)
C: Redesign role to support SELinux
E: Manage EPEL Modular repositories

* Version 0.1.4 (2020-01-08)
B: Minor Jinja2 statement fix

* Version 0.1.3 (2019-12-27)
B: Disable CentOS-CR (Continuous Release) repository by default

* Version 0.1.2 (2019-11-14)
B: Correct filename of CentOS Debuginfo repository

* Version 0.1.1 (2019-10-24)
B: Remove conflicting package task before configuring proxy and repositories

* Version 0.1.0 (2019-10-18)
F: Initial release
